<div class="language-text line-numbers-mode" data-ext="text" data-title="text"><pre v-pre class="language-text"><code>&lt;button id="btn">按钮&lt;/button>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h3 id="_2给按钮绑定事件-监听用户操作" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_2给按钮绑定事件-监听用户操作"><span>2给按钮绑定事件，监听用户操作</span></a></h3>
